{"tid":2228137,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【退黨保平安？｜美移民局禁止中共黨員申請綠卡】","createTime":"2020-10-03T10:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T10:29:39.000Z","uid":133042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5d6b53a17da8c4707ac234fd1d8e9c9a7c777974","tid":2228137,"uid":133042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gHnjAXb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgHnjAXb.jpg&h=02048a6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼美國首度將香港納入難民特別分配類別、額外提供援助之後，美國國土安全局及移民局剛剛更新簽證指引，首度針對共產黨成員，劍指中共。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"medium\"><span class=\"red\">新措施下令禁止中共黨員、甚或與中共直接或間接有關人士的移民申請，這意味一眾官二代、商二代、小粉紅、共青團成員都會有機會出事。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n相關指引涵蓋範圍相當廣泛，<span class=\"medium\"><span class=\"red\">不單是指中共黨員，同時包括中共從屬或關聯團體成員</span></span>，須知道係「一黨專政」的黨國體系底下，海外華人社團一直被視為中共海外統戰的爪牙，<span class=\"red\">2016年中共中央辦公廳亦提出歐美同學會應成立共產黨黨組，統戰中國留學生，將海外「地下黨」地面化，這或成為新措施針對對象</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次措施明顯沿用「中共不等於中國」框架，嚴格區別「中共」及「中國人民」，預計針對中共的措施會逐步收緊。<br />\n<br />\n👉訂閱Patreon，了解我的思想、工作、生活：<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/nathanlaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fnathanlaw&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdmL0CtalYwMF7My3GtbBKd0%3D&h=e212f033\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/nathanlaw</a><br />\n👉訂閱「國際戰線頻道」 零時差緊貼最新動態：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKinternationalfront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKinternationalfront&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdmL0CtalYwMF7My3GtbBKd0%3D&h=8e0075c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKinternationalfront</a>"},{"pid":"85ae1909b63b3f88b0d4f9f3793c77d500e1306e","tid":2228137,"uid":33874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:26:33.000Z","msg":"已經申咗嘅會唔會要佢取消先？"},{"pid":"0af2e351900cb19ccfe3f00add82ee192ad37960","tid":2228137,"uid":137160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":